summary: An ordinance discontinuing the eminent domain proceedings for 41st Avenue Northeast from the north line of Hawthorne Homes Addition No. 1 to the south lind of East 65th Street, and of East 62nd Street from 40th Avenue Northeast to 43rd Avenue Northeast; as contemplated by Ordinance 84397, King County Cause No. 500206; providing for the payment of taxable costs, and repealing said Ordinance 84397.
